For the Kalzium of KDE 4.0 we decided to add a local copy of libavogadro. The reason is that libavogadro is to much in flux to be used as a real library. The internal copy will be synced with the official library as often as possible without adding new features after the freeze.

For KDE 4.1 we will remove the internal copy and depend on the 

libavogadro is a lib for rendering and also editing (drawing) molecules with Qt, OpenGL and OpenBabel.

http://avogadro.sourceforge.net
